<div class="main_container">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="row justify-content-center" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom:10px; margin-top: 50px;"> 
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-10 col-lg-8" style="padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;">
        <p>본인인증 <span style="margin-left: 10px; font-weight:400;font-size: 12px;color: hsl(0, 0%, 45%); ">환전신청 전에 1회 본인인증이 필요합니다.</span></p>
